ygData.messageBody:
Hey Rob! Welcome to Rodcet Nife!!! I am running around the Oasis
right now but was planning on heading back to the Faydark area. I am
getting close to hitting level 17 and need to train in Dual Wield.

I will look for you and give you a /t if I see ya. Don't think we can
group, but I can kind of keep an eye out for ya. Have been grouping
with a few druids from my guild though so maybe they can help you out.

Alaindar (Mystic Alliance)
Half-Elf Ranger of the 16th Season


--- In EQ_rainbow@y..., rob40@a... wrote:
> Thanks everyone for the great welcome. I created a new character
> last night on Rodcet Nife, a druid his name is Dominoe if anyone is
> around I would love to group. He is in Freeport at the moment but
> unless I can get a bond I need to get back to Kel. I will be on
> tonite around 10 CST if anyone wants to help train a new druid in
the
> ways of Tunare.
>
> May Tunare smile on you all,
> Dominoe 3rd season Druid
